<section xml:id="L2" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>L2: Limits Analytically</title>
  <objectives>
    <dl>
      <li>
        <title>L2</title>
        <p>I can use limit laws and algebraic techniques to compute the one-sided or two-sided limit of a function.</p>
      </li>
    </dl>
  </objectives>
  

